Masters in International Cooperation and Humanitarian Aid

“ONLINE PROGRAMME FOR COORDINATORS OF HUMANITARIAN PROJECTS”

The Master’s in International Cooperation and Humanitarian Aid is a course developed by KALU Institute to train coordinators of projects. It covers all the aspects 
of the management of humanitarian projects. https://kaluinstitute.org/masters-in-international-cooperation-and-humanitarian-aid/

